          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-Y08B703C-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-Y08B703C-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-Y08B703C-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-1" n="1">Fair ones! to you, who Hearts command,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-2" n="2">And gently sway with Fan in Hand,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-3" n="3">Your Fav'rite Punch a Suppliant Falls,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-4" n="4">And humbly for assistance calls!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-5" n="5">He humbly calls, and begs you'll stop</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-6" n="6">The gothick Rage of Vander-Hop;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-7" n="7">Who invades without Pretense or right,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-8" n="8">Or any Law but that of Might,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-9" n="9">Our Pigmy Land── and treats our Kings</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-10" n="10">Like paltry── idle── wooden things:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-11" n="11">Has beat our Dancers out of doors;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-12" n="12">And call'd our chastest Virgins Whores.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-13" n="13">He has not left our Queen a Rag-on;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-14" n="14">Has forc'd our George away and Dragon.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-15" n="15">Has broke our Wires, not was he civil</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-16" n="16">To D<hi rend="superscript">ṛ</hi> Faustus, nor the Devil!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-17" n="17">Even me he hurried with fell Rage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-18" n="18">Most hoarsly squeaking off the Stage.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-19" n="19">And faith our Fright was very great,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-20" n="20">To see a Minister of State</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-21" n="21">Arm'd with Power and Fury, come</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-22" n="22">To force us from our little Home.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-23" n="23">We fear'd (as I am sure we'd Reason)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-24" n="24">An Accusation of High-Treason.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-25" n="25">'Till, starting up, says Bannimeer,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-26" n="26">Treason, my Friends, we need not fear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-27" n="27">For 'gainst the Brass we us'd no Pow'r,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-28" n="28">Nor strove to save the Chancellor!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-29" n="29">Nor did we show the least Affection</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-30" n="30">To Rochford on the Meath Election;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-31" n="31">Nor did we sing── M<hi rend="superscript">c̣</hi>Hugh he means!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-32" n="32">You Villain I'll dash our your Brains:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-33" n="33">'Tis no Affair of State that brings</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-34" n="34">Me here── nor Bus'ness of the Kings:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-35" n="35">I come to seize you all as Deptors,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-36" n="36">And bind you fast in Iron Fetters,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-37" n="37">From sight of every Freind in Town,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-38" n="38">'Till fifty pounds are paid me down.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-39" n="39">Fifty, quoth I, a devilish Sum!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-40" n="40">But stay 'till the Brass farthings come;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-41" n="41">Then shall we all be rich as Iews,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-42" n="42">From Castle down to lowest Stews;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-43" n="43">That Sum to you shall then be told,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-44" n="44">Tho' now we cannot furnish Gold.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-45" n="45">Add too! 'tis said that you and I</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-46" n="46">Are of the self-same Family.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-47" n="47">And Faith I'm apt to think so too;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-48" n="48">For who is liker me than you?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-49" n="49">For the same grave and awkward Grace</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-50" n="50">Shews forth itself in either Face:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-51" n="51">And each of us with Labour Struts</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-52" n="52">Behind at least a Tun of Guts:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-53" n="53">We tally well in these Respects,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-54" n="54">But best of all in Intellects;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-55" n="55">For when you made Distinction learn'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-56" n="56">'Tween the words Sorry and concern'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-57" n="57">And when upon a grave Affair,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-58" n="58">Amaz'd you gap'd behind the Chair;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-59" n="59">They cry'd how like a Punchinello</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-60" n="60">Is that same fat beef-headed Fellow?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-61" n="61">The prithee, Cousin, let us buss,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-62" n="62">And cease to treat your Kindred thus.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-63" n="63">Quoth he, thou vile misshapen Beast,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-64" n="64">Thou Knave am I become thy Iest?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-65" n="65">And dost thou think that I am come</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-66" n="66">To carry nought but Farthings home?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-67" n="67">Thou Fool! I ne'er do things by halves:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-68" n="68">Farthings were made for Irish Slaves.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-69" n="69">No Brass for me── It must be gold,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-70" n="70">Or fifty pounds in Silver told</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-71" n="71">That can by any means obtain</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-72" n="72">Freedom for thee or for thy Train.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-73" n="73"><lb/>Votre tres humble Serviteur,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-74" n="74">I'm not in Iest, said I, I'm sure;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-75" n="75">But from the Bottom of my Belly,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-76" n="76">I, in sober Sadness tell you,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-77" n="77">I thought it was good Reasoning,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-78" n="78">For us fictitious Men to bring</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-79" n="79">Brass Counters made by William Wood, 3}</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-80" n="80">Which might as well be understood</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-81" n="81">Intrinsick, as we Flesh and Blood.──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-82" n="82">Then since we are but mimick Men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-83" n="83">Pray let us pay in mimick Coin.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-84" n="84"><lb/>Quoth he, thou lovest, Punch, to prate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-85" n="85">And coud for ever hold Debate:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-86" n="86">But think'st thou that I've nought to do</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-87" n="87">But to stand prating thus with you?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-88" n="88">Therefore to stop your noisy Parly,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-89" n="89">I at once assure you fairly;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-90" n="90">That not a Puppet of you all</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-91" n="91">Shall stir a Step without this Wall;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-92" n="92">Nor merry Andrew beat thy Drum,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-93" n="93">Untill you pay th' aforesaid Sum.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-94" n="94"><lb/>Then marching off with swiftest Pace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-95" n="95">To write Despatches for his Grace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-96" n="96">The Revel-Master left the Room,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-97" n="97">And us condemn'd to fatal Doom.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-98" n="98"><lb/>Now, Fair ones! if I e'er found Grace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-99" n="99">Or if my Iokes did ever please,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-100" n="100">Use all your Interest with the Sec────</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-101" n="101">They say he's at the Ladies Beck.──</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-102" n="102">And tho' he thirsts as much for Gold</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-103" n="103">As ever Midas did of old,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-104" n="104">Your charms I'm sure can never fail</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-105" n="105">Your Eyes must influence, must prevail:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-106" n="106">At your Command he'll set us free;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-107" n="107">Let us to you owe Liberty;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-108" n="108">Get us a License now to play,</l>
            <l rend="center" xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-109" n="109">And We in Duty bound will pray.<lb/>_Punch cum Sociis</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y08B703C-line-110" n="110">om.</l>
